// train_model.uniL — Train UniNN from Scratch
// Complete example: data generation → model creation → training → evaluation → save
//
// Demonstrates:
//   - Custom tensor operations
//   - Building a neural network from custom neurons
//   - Training with Adam optimizer
//   - Multi-class classification on synthetic dataset
//   - Model serialization for publishing
//
